# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../main_window.rst:43
msgid "Play-head / Ruler"
msgstr "Playhead / Penggaris"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../main_window.rst:43
msgid ""
"The ruler shows the time-scale, and the red line is the play-head. The play-"
"head represents the current playback position. Hold :kbd:`Shift` key while "
"dragging the playhead to snap to nearby clips."
msgstr ""
"Penggaris menunjukkan skala waktu, dan garis merah adalah playhead. Playhead "
"menunjukkan posisi pemutaran saat ini. Tahan tombol :kbd:`Shift` saat "
"menyeret playhead untuk menempel pada klip di dekatnya."

