# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../main_window.rst:314
msgid "High DPI / 4K Monitors"
msgstr "Monitor High DPI / 4K"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../main_window.rst:316
msgid ""
"OpenShot Video Editor provides robust support for High DPI (Dots Per Inch) "
"monitors, ensuring that the interface looks sharp and is easily readable on "
"displays with various DPI settings. This support is particularly beneficial "
"for users with 4K monitors or other high-resolution displays."
msgstr ""
"OpenShot Video Editor menyediakan dukungan kuat untuk monitor High DPI (Dots "
"Per Inch), memastikan antarmuka terlihat tajam dan mudah dibaca pada layar "
"dengan berbagai pengaturan DPI. Dukungan ini sangat bermanfaat bagi pengguna "
"dengan monitor 4K atau layar resolusi tinggi lainnya."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../main_window.rst:321
msgid "Per Monitor DPI Awareness"
msgstr "Kesadaran DPI Per Monitor"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../main_window.rst:323
msgid ""
"OpenShot is DPI aware on a per-monitor basis, meaning it can adjust its "
"scaling dynamically depending on the DPI settings of each connected monitor. "
"This ensures a consistent and high-quality user experience across different "
"displays."
msgstr ""
"OpenShot sadar DPI berdasarkan setiap monitor, artinya dapat menyesuaikan "
"skala secara dinamis tergantung pengaturan DPI dari setiap monitor yang "
"terhubung. Ini memastikan pengalaman pengguna yang konsisten dan berkualitas "
"tinggi di berbagai layar."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../main_window.rst:327
msgid "DPI Scaling on Windows"
msgstr "Skala DPI di Windows"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../main_window.rst:329
msgid ""
"On Windows, OpenShot rounds the scaling factor to the nearest whole value to "
"maintain visual integrity. This rounding helps avoid visual artifacts in the "
"UI rendering and ensures that the interface elements remain crisp and well-"
"aligned. Due to this rounding, scaling options can sometimes lead to "
"increased font-sizes and a feeling that the UI elements are a bit too large."
msgstr ""
"Di Windows, OpenShot membulatkan faktor skala ke nilai bulat terdekat untuk "
"menjaga integritas visual. Pembulatan ini membantu menghindari artefak "
"visual pada rendering UI dan memastikan elemen antarmuka tetap tajam dan "
"teratur. Karena pembulatan ini, opsi skala terkadang menyebabkan ukuran font "
"meningkat dan elemen UI terasa sedikit terlalu besar."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../main_window.rst:334
msgid "**125% scaling** rounds to **100%**"
msgstr "**Skala 125%** dibulatkan menjadi **100%**"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../main_window.rst:335
msgid "**150% scaling** rounds to **200%**"
msgstr "**Skala 150%** dibulatkan menjadi **200%**"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../main_window.rst:338
msgid "Workarounds for Fine-Grained Adjustment"
msgstr "Solusi untuk Penyesuaian Presisi"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../main_window.rst:340
msgid ""
"While rounding helps maintain a clean interface, there are workarounds for "
"users who require more precise control over the scaling. However, these "
"methods are **not recommended** due to potential visual artifacts:"
msgstr ""
"Meskipun pembulatan membantu menjaga antarmuka tetap bersih, ada solusi bagi "
"pengguna yang membutuhkan kontrol lebih presisi atas skala. Namun, metode "
"ini **tidak disarankan** karena potensi artefak visual:"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../main_window.rst:343
msgid "**QT_SCALE_FACTOR_ROUNDING_POLICY=PassThrough**"
msgstr "**QT_SCALE_FACTOR_ROUNDING_POLICY=PassThrough**"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../main_window.rst:345
msgid ""
"Setting this environment variable can disable rounding and allow more "
"precise scaling."
msgstr ""
"Mengatur variabel lingkungan ini dapat menonaktifkan pembulatan dan "
"memungkinkan skala yang lebih presisi."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../main_window.rst:346
msgid ""
"**Note:** This may cause visual artifacts, particularly in the timeline, and "
"is not recommended."
msgstr ""
"**Catatan:** Ini dapat menyebabkan artefak visual, terutama di timeline, dan "
"tidak disarankan."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../main_window.rst:348
msgid "**QT_SCALE_FACTOR=1.25** (or similar value)"
msgstr "**QT_SCALE_FACTOR=1.25** (atau nilai serupa)"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../main_window.rst:350
msgid ""
"Manually setting the scale factor can provide finer adjustments to the font "
"and UI scaling."
msgstr ""
"Mengatur faktor skala secara manual dapat memberikan penyesuaian lebih halus "
"pada skala font dan UI."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../main_window.rst:351
msgid ""
"This can also be set via Preferences (User Interface Scale) - but expect "
"border/line issues on Windows with fractional scales."
msgstr ""
"Ini juga dapat diatur melalui Preferensi (Skala Antarmuka Pengguna) - tetapi "
"harapkan masalah garis/batas pada Windows dengan skala pecahan."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../main_window.rst:352
msgid ""
"**Note:** This method can also lead to visual artifacts and make OpenShot "
"harder to use."
msgstr ""
"**Catatan:** Metode ini juga dapat menyebabkan artefak visual dan membuat "
"OpenShot lebih sulit digunakan."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../main_window.rst:354
msgid ""
"For more info on adjusting these environment variables, please visit https://"
"github.com/OpenShot/openshot-qt/wiki/OpenShot-UI-too-large."
msgstr ""
"Untuk informasi lebih lanjut tentang penyesuaian variabel lingkungan ini, "
"silakan kunjungi https://github.com/OpenShot/openshot-qt/wiki/OpenShot-UI-"
"too-large."
